# Deployment Protection

- These files affect **Vercel** production and PWA behavior for all users.
- Do not change ports, domains, CSP, or service worker caching casually.
- Any edit must consider staging Supabase vs production Supabase env vars on Vercel.
- Prefer minimal, explicit, justified changes.
- Flag rollout risk before changing deployment-sensitive behavior.
- Production stack is Vercel (frontend) + Supabase (backend).
